      "title": "I Built a Fitness Tracker for How You Speak",
      "url": "https://www.productcoalition.com/p/i-built-a-fitness-tracker-for-how",
      "source": "Product Coalition",
      "type": "article",
      "date": "2026-04-12T16:15:43+00:00",
      "summary": "The founder of ExecReps.ai shares how they overcame the 'Gulf of Evaluation' problem — showing users too much data with too little meaning. After building an impressive analytics dashboard, they realised users couldn't answer a simple question: am I improving? The key PM lesson is that users want answers, not data, and simplicity in measurement design drives better outcomes than comprehensiveness.",
