      "type": "trend",
      "date": "2026-04-09T10:00:00+00:00",
      "summary": "The NYT CEO discusses the company's strategy of doubling down on human expertise and trusted journalism as a competitive moat against AI-generated content. She argues that in a world of abundant AI content, scarcity of credible human expertise becomes the premium product. PMs in media or content-adjacent products will find this a valuable case study in differentiation strategy.",
