      "title": "How will OpenAI compete?",
      "url": "https://www.ben-evans.com/benedictevans/2026/2/19/how-will-openai-compete-nkg2x",
      "source": "Benedict Evans",
      "type": "trend",
      "date": "2026-02-19T20:51:04+00:00",
      "summary": "Benedict Evans argues that OpenAI faces four fundamental strategic challenges: no clear competitive moat, a rapidly shifting product landscape, the need to cross the chasm without existing distribution, and the difficulty of building consumer products on top of commodity models. He questions whether OpenAI's massive user base translates into durable strategic advantage. A clear-eyed analysis of the competitive dynamics shaping the AI product landscape.",
