      "url": "https://www.svpg.com/product-coaching-and-ai/",
      "source": "SVPG",
      "type": "article",
      "date": "2026-02-04T19:28:20+00:00",
      "summary": "Marty Cagan explores how AI is changing the nature of product coaching and mentorship, arguing that while AI can accelerate skill development in some areas, the fundamentally human aspects of product leadership — judgement, empathy, and stakeholder navigation — remain beyond AI's reach. He suggests coaches should focus on these irreplaceable skills rather than competing with AI on technical knowledge. A thoughtful perspective for PMs investing in their own development.",
