      "url": "https://www.ben-evans.com/benedictevans/2025/11/23/ai-networks-and-mechanical-turks",
      "source": "Benedict Evans",
      "type": "trend",
      "date": "2025-11-23T13:14:03+00:00",
      "summary": "Benedict Evans argues that LLMs represent a step change in how consumer platforms understand user behaviour — moving from correlation-based recommendations to something closer to genuine semantic understanding. This unlocks new kinds of network effects and personalisation that weren't possible with traditional ML. PMs building recommendation systems or personalisation features should understand how this shift changes the competitive landscape.",
